reviews.review_text:
Stranger Scarlet Fire I had this on cassette in late 80s. My favorite version of Stranger until that spring 90 version came along thats featured on Without A Net. Great job adjusting the low end. Phil really shows up nicely. A very well played show and you can hear Jer's enthusiasm throughout, particularly when he total rips it in Scarlet. Listen to it and you'll know.
Thanks again to all you sound wizards making these sources sound so freaking good!
